OL,3,CFormer councillor jailed after
OL,4,C'shocking and violent attack' on wife
OL,6,FA former Bridgend town councillor has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed after stabbing his wife
OL,8,Fthree times.
OL,10,FDarren Brown, 35, was convicted of
OL,11,Fattempted murder by a jury at at
OL,12,FMerthyr Tydfil Crown Court.
OL,14,FBrown was separated from his wife but
OL,15,Fremained living in the same property.
OL,16,FOn 10 July 2023 the two were arguing
OL,17,Fwhen he went downstairs and took a
OL,18,Fknife from the kitchen.
