OL,6,FHe returned upstairs and whilst his
OL,7,Fwife was trying to settle the baby
OL,8,Fdown, he stabbed her twice in the back.
OL,10,FThe victim managed to get to the
OL,11,Fbathroom and lock the door but Brown
OL,12,Fkicked the door so hard it came off
OL,13,Fits hinges.
OL,15,FThe victim was then stabbed a third
OL,16,Ftime to the back.
OL,18,FBrown also attempted to stab her in
OL,19,Fthe neck and telling her to stab him
OL,20,Fand that they would 'go together'.
