OL,6,FShe was taken to hospital where it was
OL,7,Fdiscovered she had sustained a
OL,8,Fpunctured lung.
OL,10,FShe has since made a full recovery.
OL,12,FInitially, Darren Brown said it was
OL,13,Fhis wife who had the knife and he
OL,14,Ftried to take it off her, during which
OL,15,Fshe was injured.
OL,17,FHe later pleaded guilty at court to
OL,18,Fwounding with intent but denied
OL,19,Fattempted murder.
