OL,6,FHowever, he was convicted of the
OL,7,Foffence following trial, after the
OL,8,Fjury had heard all the evidence.
OL,10,FDuring police searches of the address,
OL,11,Fit became evident that, despite no
OL,12,Fprevious reports, Brown had subjected
OL,13,Fthe victim to years of controlling
OL,14,Fbehaviour.
OL,16,FThere were locks on the exterior of
OL,17,Fevery door in the house and evidence
OL,18,Fthat there had been internal CCTV
OL,19,Fcameras.
