OL,6,FOne camera was hidden under the
OL,7,Fbedside table in the victim's bedroom
OL,8,Fand left active.
OL,10,FInvestigations found that this camera,
OL,11,Fwhich included audio, had recorded the
OL,12,Fattack on the victim as well as the
OL,13,Faftermath.
OL,15,FHannah West of the CPS said: "This was
OL,16,Fa shocking and violent attack. Darren
OL,17,FBrown deliberately obtained the knife
OL,18,Fand brought it upstairs with him,
OL,19,Fusing it when the victim was at her
OL,20,Fmost vulnerable.
