OL,6,F"Any one of the wounds could have been
OL,7,Ffatal and the evidence we presented to
OL,8,Fthe jury demonstrated Brown's
OL,9,Fintention was to kill his wife.
OL,11,F"It is difficult to imagine how
OL,12,Fterrifying this must have been for the
OL,13,Fvictim. Our thoughts remain with her
OL,14,Fand we hope she can take comfort from
OL,15,Fknowing her husband has been brought
OL,16,Fto justice for this appalling attack."
