OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Owain Morrison
OL,8,Fsaid: "This was a sustained attack
OL,9,Fwhich sought to take the life of
OL,10,FCorrine Brown.
OL,12,F"The audio recording proved crucial
OL,13,Fevidence in the case as it
OL,14,Fcorroborated the victim's account and
OL,15,Fa number of key facts that she had
OL,16,Fmentioned during her interview could
OL,17,Fbe heard on the recording, including
OL,18,Fthe suspect kicking the bathroom door
OL,19,Fthrough after the victim had sought
OL,20,Frefuge there.
