OL,6,F"Luckily the children are too young to
OL,7,Funderstand what happened. One day I
OL,8,Fwill have to explain to them that
OL,9,Ftheir father tried to kill me. I
OL,10,Fdidn't rob Darren of his future and
OL,11,Ftime with his children.
OL,13,F"He did that." Ms Brown added her
OL,14,Fchildren have kept her going
OL,15,F"throughout this horrible time".
OL,17,FDarren Brown was sentenced to 18 years
OL,18,Fand was given an indefinite
OL,19,Frestraining order to protect his
OL,20,Fvictim.
